When a mother oversteps her sons boundaries makes all the decisions for him and forces him to be by her side at all times

00:00:38.780 --> 00:00:42.309
It leaves him very little room to grow independent as he gets older in

00:00:42.829 --> 00:00:47.439
Fact his mother may work harder to make him feel guilty if he doesn't stay in touch with her constantly

00:00:47.719 --> 00:00:54.219
the son is often empathetic kind-hearted and giving but his mother often takes advantage of him because of that as

00:00:54.440 --> 00:01:00.850
