00:01:01.820 --> 00:01:07.000
Number two mother and lover if a mother lost her husband her partner unexpectedly

00:01:07.220 --> 00:01:10.119
weather from death divorce or emotional distance

00:01:10.460 --> 00:01:13.839
She might try to replace him with her son by having him play the spouse role

00:01:13.840 --> 00:01:15.409
The son will likely feel

00:01:15.409 --> 00:01:20.739
Uncomfortable fulfilling his mother's needs and may resent the father for leaving them or not being more active in their everyday lives

00:01:21.260 --> 00:01:26.529
No one should have to bear the burden of carrying on extra responsibilities. Especially starting at such a young age

00:01:26.960 --> 00:01:29.529
This can harm him both emotionally and psychologically

00:01:30.140 --> 00:01:34.089
Putting his individuality at risk number three the absent mother

00:01:34.610 --> 00:01:40.419
It can create some serious damage when a mother is absent in her son's life, especially when her son is young

00:01:41.060 --> 00:01:47.409
According to hope Edelman author of motherless daughters those who grew up without a mother can have trouble forming relationships with others

00:01:47.869 --> 00:01:50.438
sons who grew up without mothers often either blame themselves

00:01:50.900 --> 00:01:54.909
Believing they did something wrong that caused their mother to leave or they end up resenting them

00:01:55.130 --> 00:01:58.030
It's easier to hold on to anger than nothing at all

00:01:59.119 --> 00:02:05.049
Number four the boss and subordinate this type of relationship very much takes on the my way or the highway attitude

00:02:05.540 --> 00:02:09.939
The mother is often highly controlling and dominant forcing her son to follow her every lead

00:02:10.250 --> 00:02:16.509
He is little to no say in expressing his sense of self. He will also have difficulty making decisions as he gets older

00:02:17.140 --> 00:02:19.929
this can either influenced him to depend on others too much or

00:02:20.420 --> 00:02:24.910
He'll mirror his mother's actions and take control in situations where he feels valued and heard

00:02:26.209 --> 00:02:31.119
Number five the hide-and-seek mom this type of mom is often emotionally distant

00:02:31.280 --> 00:02:33.789
Her son has a hard time reaching her when he needs it the most

00:02:34.250 --> 00:02:38.770
She can be highly unpredictable with her mood swings which makes it hard for her son to get close to her

00:02:38.770 --> 00:02:40.720
I'm sure of how she'll react

